{"tid":387773,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"2017-09-05 每日一屌張寶欣","createTime":"2017-09-05T01:58:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T14:00:37.000Z","uid":92376,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7f35202862b0f610aad3aca0a4a674cf5f6ec3f4","tid":387773,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T01:58:46.000Z","msg":"BBC最受歡迎香港小姐數據分析<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/024412_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F024412_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=257bb87e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n根據mytv個時間 17:42個陣10號個累積數量係704990<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/024504_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F024504_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=deb3a36e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n19:13個陣10號個累積數量係757943<br />\n<br />\n總時間長度=19:13-17:42=91秒<br />\n數量增長=757943-704990=52953<br />\n增長速率=52953/91=582/秒<br />\n<br />\n根據賽前BBC記錄 10號同9號有明顯差距<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/04/024922_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F04%2F024922_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=c861a540&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n10號同9號差距=1768205-698644=1069561<br />\n<br />\n假設10號一直保持同一個速率去追<br />\n假設9號今晚完全冇增長<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">10號超越9號所需時間=1069561/582=1838秒=31分鐘</span><br />\n<br />\n成個環節頭尾應該冇30分鐘 仲要未計9號今晚個增長 <br />\n完全睇唔到10號會贏個可能性<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n----------------------<br />\n<strong>蘋果日報--【唔公平?】超專業分析 網友 : 最受歡迎港姐無可能係張寶欣</strong><br />\n<a href=\"https://is.gd/bBrel3\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fis.gd%2FbBrel3&d=T6xoQvd6NSR2GGzZF4vtHbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=e8d15715\" target=\"_blank\">https://is.gd/bBrel3</a><br />\n<br />\n今年香港小姐競選決賽不斷Hard Sell大台直播App，就連友誼小姐一獎都改做「big big channel最受歡迎香港小姐」。此獎項以直播App上網友給的心心作標準，稱以最高心心數量的佳麗奪得，最後獎項由10號張寶欣獲得。先不論有大量網友投訴直播App在比賽其間完全不能開啟，既然這麼多人未能連線，那心心從哪裡來可說是個迷。賽前被網友極力支持的9號金美黎，不但三甲不入，就連「BBC最受歡迎港姐」都拿不到令他們心心不忿。有網友製作圖表加上超專業的數據分析指出獎項根本不應由10號張寶欣獲得，獲獎的該是9號金美黎，指比賽有不公之嫌。 <br />\n<br />\n延伸閱讀: <strong>香港01【港姐2017】張寶欣Big Big Channel心心疑造假　金美黎輸得唔抵</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hk01.com/娛樂/116762/-港姐2017-張寶欣Big-Big-Channel心心疑造假-金美黎輸得唔抵\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82%2F116762%2F-%E6%B8%AF%E5%A7%902017-%E5%BC%B5%E5%AF%B6%E6%AC%A3Big-Big-Channel%E5%BF%83%E5%BF%83%E7%96%91%E9%80%A0%E5%81%87-%E9%87%91%E7%BE%8E%E9%BB%8E%E8%BC%B8%E5%BE%97%E5%94%94%E6%8A%B5&d=T6xoQvd6NSR2GGzZF4vtHbIOlR6kLHi1VdsYCD5DrTY%3D&h=44a39cf5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hk01.com/娛樂/116762/-港姐2017-張寶欣Big-Big-Channel心心疑造假-金美黎輸得唔抵</a><br />\n<br />\n今日係你拎左人個獎既第3日，咁樣喺人地個乞衣兜度嗱飯食，你呢兩晚訓得心安嗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你放心，你咁偉大既功績我會每日同大家講一次，等大家知道你點樣喺個幾兩個月以黎都大幅度落後之下，最後喺現場果半個鐘都無既時間拎到百幾萬票反先奪獎既威水史，叻呀你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b58be2b777aa44afd8208067d265008228bb61d4","tid":387773,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T01:59:50.000Z","msg":"吳若希 我懂的"},{"pid":"e306cb68630cf32e91963cba6d5524b66544d3bf","tid":387773,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T01:59:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"12cb1c5c4a7df3ffe0d592f5c3c80b25bf6b83b0","tid":387773,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T02:07:20.000Z","msg":"張寶欣我屌你老母臭化閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"697f61ba90f3006ef86f530f16c5fc3845d267ee","tid":387773,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T02:12:27.000Z","msg":"覺唔覺得男人老狗咁在意個垃圾電視show好撚戇鳩"},{"pid":"fa43f17bc4518facdabfcb44e6aa4b9caeadeeea","tid":387773,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T05:43:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae24bbdf484ddfa3e5f1157cfb93038d36baf32","tid":387773,"uid":98386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T05:46:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>覺唔覺得男人老狗咁在意個垃圾電視show好撚戇鳩</blockquote><br />\n日日推尻金美黎唔知想點"},{"pid":"51b57dac1820d9924d50500ef6601f31cc926504","tid":387773,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T06:27:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>覺唔覺得男人老狗咁在意個垃圾電視show好撚戇鳩</blockquote><br />\n日日推尻金美黎唔知想點</blockquote><br />\n佢如果行得正企得正既駛驚鳩人講?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffe204542ffd3868d859ee47c9bedeef6f613795","tid":387773,"uid":137470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T06:49:19.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d03e22b72bcace3925209826bfae2efd59407750","tid":387773,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T07:03:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n啱呀,今日佢搶人豬肉獎<br />\n他日可以搶其他野<br />\n搶角色,搶女飛躍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算佢可以繼續隻手遮天都好,都起碼要比人知道